snippet.title: DOLL EYE CHAPTER 1| OFFICIAL TRAILER
snippet.description:
ALFRED PLUSHIES: https://makeship.com/products/alfred-dolleye
(Campaign ends on the 20th of November)
DOLL EYE: https://twisted-doctor.itch.io/doll-eye-chapter-1 

MUSIC BY:
Trailer song: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCKVKm_lu9A8bbSX4RS67f2g
Plush ad song: https://soundcloud.com/telebasher
(The music used has been commissioned by me for this project, please do not make use of it unless the artists state to be comfortable with you doing so)

---

After about a year and 3 months worth of work... It is finally done!
This is my first big project on RPG maker MV and I'm so excited to show you all the content I have worked on in this one :-)

"Doll Eye - Chapter one" is the first part of a dialogue based, story-driven psychological horror game made on RPG Maker MV
This game features original art/music and is about one hour long. This might depend on your reading speed, how many things you check,  your choices, etc.
This game has one ending
Doll Eye is aimed at an audience of individuals that are 15+
More info: https://twisted-doctor.itch.io/doll-eye-chapter-1

---

SUPPORT ME: https://www.patreon.com/twisted_doctor

YOUTUBE: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCFLlz5_bxaijqvoTl-N3KAg

SIDE YOUTUBE: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCAoL-6iYBrWeJo4wGxXEUXw

MERCH: https://teespring.com/stores/twisted-doctor

TWITTER: https://twitter.com/twiisted_doctor

DEVIANTART: https://www.deviantart.com/twisted-doctor

CHARACTER BIOS: https://toyhou.se/twisted-doctor

SOUNDCLOUD: https://soundcloud.com/nasty-doctor

---

PLEASE BE NICE TO ME ....... It's a free-to-play rpg maker game made by a teenager ... and if u expect too much from it . don't :-(
